### Technical Decisions
1. **Library Compatibility**: Resolved Docker/go-containerregistry version mismatch by using Docker v27.5.1 + go-containerregistry v0.20.2
2. **Image Parsing**: Used `name.ParseReference()` for flexible image name handling (supports tags and digests)
3. **OCI Conversion**: Used `daemon.Image()` with context propagation for cancellation support
4. **Security**: Implemented robust command injection prevention with character validation

